    <!-- About Activity -->
    <string name="about_how_title">How it Works</string>
    <string name="about_desc_flashcards">Memora uses the simplest and most efficient method of leaning words in a new language:
        \n\nFlashcards.
        \n\nFlashcards can be used to learn simple things like nouns, verbs, or adjectives. They
        can also be used to study whole phrases at a time, or even for practicing verb conjugations.</string>
    <string name="about_why_title">Why it Works</string>
    <string name="about_desc_time">Memora will track which words you feel comfortable with and which
        you need to practice. Each time a word appears, you get to select how confident you are with
        that word. Options are: "Easy", "Medium", "Hard", or "Critical". Easy words
        are shown to you less often than Hard words. Critical words are always shown.
        \n\nYou can also study specific Categories of words regardless of when the individual words
        are due for review by selecting "Study Category" from the Main Menu.</string>

